{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A humble black pawn decided to challenge the first rule of chess. The white pieces were not happy about this at all. The result? War.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434710/extras/gif1.gif?t=1739453800\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A PAWN WITH A GOAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control the black pawn across various chessboards, following the rules of movement, defense, and attack from classical chess but with a twist: the black pawn has the movement capabilities of a king and can push black pieces, commanding them to attack on your orders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434710/extras/gifA.gif?t=1739453800\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A SHOP TO GEAR UP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The pawn is not alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434710/extras/gifb.gif?t=1739453800\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>YOUR BRAIN WILL MELT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The puzzles will require logical thinking, agility, and creativity to find solutions and achieve the objective of each level (there are 60 levels with progressively increasing difficulty).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434710/extras/gifC.gif?t=1739453800\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is also a story mode with a world map, collectibles, and an item shop, where you can gather money to purchase upgrades as you progress through the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Innovative chess-based game with a captivating story of rebellion.</strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3434710?t=17394538